snippet.title: Myth of Empires Official V1.0 Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Myth of Empires, Wishlist NOW on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1371580
Join Our Discord:
discord.gg/mythofempires

Myth of Empires is a multiplayer war sandbox game featuring a high degree of freedom. Players must survive, craft, create, and lead troops in their quest to conquer territory and build their own empire. Myth of Empires v1.0 will be released on February 21, 2024.
